      public void construct()
      Description copied from class: OperationMode
      The method to be called at the start of the OperationMode's operation, after the INIT button is pressed but before the PLAY button is pressed. This will run once. You do not need to call LinearOpMode.waitForStart(), the OperationMode will do this automatically after this method is finished.
